          <ul class="services-list">
            <li>Cost-efficient bulk recycling and logistics planning</li>
            <li>Compliance with EPA and sustainability standards</li>
            <li>Circular economy outcomes for public asset recovery</li>
            <li>Nationwide collection and processing capacity</li>
            <li>Customised services for council facilities, schools, libraries, and housing programs</li>
          </ul>

