                <h4>Boost Environmental Performance</h4>
                <ul class="impact-list">
                  <li>Recover valuable materials like aluminium, silicon, and glass</li>
                  <li>Divert solar waste from landfill</li>
                  <li>Report on emissions reduction and landfill avoidance</li>
